STATE of North Carolina
v.
Anthony WILLIAMS. No. 369P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2006. Anthony Williams, Pro Se. Wendy L. Greene, Assistant Attorney General, Peter S. Gilchrist, III, District Attorney for State of NC. Prior report: ___ N.C.App. ___, 630 S.E.2d 216 .

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 11th day of July 2006 by Defendant in this matter for request for review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th day of August 2006."
